===Noun===
'''saliva'''

# {{physiology}} A clear, slightly alkaline liquid secreted into the mouth by the [[salivary gland]]s and [[mucous gland]]s, consisting of water, [[mucin]], [[protein]], and [[enzyme]]s, It moistens the mouth, lubricates ingested food, and begins the breakdown of [[starch]]es.

